## Overview

This is a Java/Spring Boot LLM-powered MCP Mesh agent. It uses mesh delegation to access an LLM provider.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Java 17+
- Maven 3.9+
- An LLM provider agent running on the mesh

### Running the Agent

` + "```" + `bash
mvn spring-boot:run
` + "```" + `

Or with meshctl:

` + "```" + `bash
meshctl start {{ .Name }}
` + "```" + `

The agent will start on port {{ .Port }} by default.

## Architecture

This agent uses `@MeshLlm` to delegate LLM calls to a provider agent on the mesh network.

